Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.33,0:24:12.65,Default,EVA,0,0,0,,Tell me your name, mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.30,0:24:16.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（潤一郎）\Nほら　お菓子もあるんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.36,0:24:15.76,Default,JUN,0,0,0,,See? I have snacks, too.
